# 1) Initialization
units lj
dimension 3
atom_style atomic
boundary p p p
# 2) System definition
# 3) Settings
mass 1 1.0
mass 2 10.0
pair_style lj/cut 4.0
pair_coeff 1 1 1.0 1.0
pair_coeff 2 2 0.5 3.0
# 4) Monitoring
thermo 10
thermo_style custom step etotal press
# 5) Run
minimize 1.0e-6 1.0e-6 1000 10000
